title: The Beatles - The Alternate 1 (Compiled and remastered by den0iZ
description:
The Beatles - The Alternative 1


Do you know The Beatles - 1 album? Well, this is the same, but with different versions, mixes and takes of these songs, also from live performances....

So, den0iZer has done his first contribution and response on all alternate versions of Beatles&#039; albums, done by many bootlegers.

But the original 1 album is the same, nothing new, but another compilation ;)
